{"word":"H6960 - קָוָה - qâvâh - kaw-vaw' - Gather","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קָוָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>qâvâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kaw-vaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Gather"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - காத்திரு, சேர், நம்பிக்கைவை, எதிர்பார்த்திரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1) to wait, to look for, to hope, to expect"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) waiting (participle)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to wait or to look eagerly for"},{"paragraph":"2) to lie in wait for"},{"paragraph":"3) to wait for, to linger for"},{"paragraph":"2) to collect, to bind together; (Niphal) to be collected"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>bind</i> together (perhaps by <i>twisting</i>), that is, <i>collect</i>; (figuratively) to <i>expect: - </i>gather (together), look, patiently, tarry, wait (for, on, upon)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4723 - מִקְוֶה - miqveh - mik-veh'/4723\">H4723</a>, <a href=\"#/H4724 - מִקְוָה - miqvâh - mik-vaw'/4724\">H4724</a>, <a href=\"#/H6957 - קַו - qav - kav/6957\">H6957</a>, <a href=\"#/H6960 - קָוָה - qâvâh - kaw-vaw'/6960\">H6960</a>, <a href=\"#/H6961 - קָוֶה - qâveh - kaw-veh'/6961\">H6961</a>, <a href=\"#/H6978 - קַו־קַו - qav-qav - kav-kav'/6978\">H6978</a>, <a href=\"#/H8445 - תֹּוקַהַת - Tôwqahath - to-kah'-ath/8445\">H8445</a>, <a href=\"#/H8615 - תִּקְוָה - tiqvâh - tik-vaw'/8615\">H8615</a>, <a href=\"#/H8616 - תִּקְוָה - Tiqvâh - tik-vaw'/8616\">H8616</a>"}]}